tag name|||Synth Riders: Zardonic - "Blue Monday (Synth Riders version)
tag jj|||Synth Riders goes “Back to the Synths” to celebrate 5 years of riding the rails with the “Synthwave Essentials Volume 3” music pack!  Headlined by The Midnight, this 10 song pack (5 free songs, 5 paid DLC) also features a brand new cover of New Order’s classic “Blue Monday”, created just for Synth Riders by legendary DJ Zardonic!  Enjoy these great tracks in “Back to the Synths”, one of our original play Stages which has received a special “glow-up” to coincide with our birthday!Add “Blue Monday” (Synth Riders version) by Zardonic (feat. REEBZ) to your library!This classic from electronic music pioneers New Order is given Zardonic’s signature heavy EDM treatment, with rocking drums and guitar, blended with EDM and lashings of retro synths over REEBZ’ vocals. Made specifically for Synth Riders, expect a heavy new twist on an old favorite.
